divs: sighting detailsthis morning(oct 06, 2010)one of our drafters and i went out to watch the space station fly over. it was to come over at 6:43am. he asked where we would first see it. so i pointed. *(wit's name deleted--cms\sg)said, "there it is!". so i looked up to see what he had spotted. it was not the space station, but another ufo (my first sighting was on sept 22, 2010). we watched as it zig-zagged and did circles in the sky, until we lost site of it. freaky! oh yes, we also watched the space station. it's trajectory was a bit lackluster as compared to what we just saw. with this being my second sighting it has answered a big question in my mind. however it raises many more. did the guys in the iss see it. i'm sure the government is aware of these objects. why do they not share the information with us? who are they? why are they here? what do they want? are they a threat?
Summary: UFO sighting prior to ISS sighting
